    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in good condition overall. It runs and drives well with no major mechanical issues, though it may have minor wear consistent with normal use. The exterior shows some light surface scratches or minor blemishes but no significant dents or structural damage. The interior is reasonably clean and functional with typical signs of use.",
